  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng d\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng v\u1EADt kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i l\xE0 th\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m ta ganh t\u1EE9c, d\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng t\u01B0\u1EE3ng ch\u1EA1m kh\xF4ng ra g\xEC \u0111\u1EC3 ch\u1ECDc gi\u1EADn ta. Cho n\xEAn ta s\u1EBD d\xF9ng nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i l\xE0 d\xE2n ta \u0111\u1EC3 khi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng n\xF3 ganh t\u1EE9c; Ta s\u1EBD d\xF9ng m\u1ED9t d\xE2n kh\xF4ng hi\u1EC3u bi\u1EBFt \u0111\u1EBF khi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng t\u1EE9c gi\u1EADn. "), mdx("h6", {
