  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "Trong ph\u1ED1 s\u1EBD c\xF3 g\u01B0\u01A1m gi\xE1o; trong nh\xE0 ch\xFAng s\u1EBD c\xF3 s\u1EF1 kinh ho\xE0ng. Thanh ni\xEAn, thi\u1EBFu n\u1EEF s\u1EBD ch\u1EBFt, H\xE0i nhi v\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gi\xE0 c\u1EA3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ED3ng chung s\u1ED1 ph\u1EADn. "), mdx("h6", {
