  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng ta kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n k\u1EBB th\xF9 ch\xFAng hu\xEAnh hoang; v\xEC k\u1EBB th\xF9 ch\xFAng s\u1EBD l\u1EA7m t\u01B0\u1EDFng v\xE0 khoe khoang r\u1EB1ng, 'Ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE3 th\u1EAFng r\u1ED3i! CH\xDAA kh\xF4ng c\xF3 \u0111\xF3ng vai tr\xF2 g\xEC trong vi\u1EC7c n\u1EA7y c\u1EA3.' "), mdx("h6", {
